definitions.definition: Of, related to, intended for or involving the anus .
Of the stage in psychosexual development when the child's interest is alleged to be concentrated on the anal region.
Of a person, compulsive and stubborn , obsessed with neatness and accuracy (usually in an egosyntonic way), supposedly from not having progressed beyond the anal stage .
examples: Please don't touch his furniture, as he can get very anal about things like that.

definitions.definition: Of tasks, questions, subject matter, etc., obsessively fussy or precise.
examples: This questionnaire goes into the most ridiculous amount of detail. It's totally anal .

main_definition: ( not comparable ) Of, related to, intended for or involving the anus . [from 18th c.]
secondary_definitions: ( psychoanalysis ) Of the stage in psychosexual development when the child's interest is alleged to be concentrated on the anal region. [from 20th c.]

( psychology , also vulgar informal ) Of a person, compulsive and stubborn , obsessed with neatness and accuracy (usually in an egosyntonic way), supposedly from not having progressed beyond the anal stage . [from 20th c.]
( informal , vulgar ) Of tasks, questions, subject matter, etc., obsessively fussy or precise.
( entomology , of a vein ) Proximate to the thorax .
